OL,6,FFootage released by Northumbria Police
OL,7,Fcaptures the moment an intruder breaks
OL,8,Fthrough a shop ceiling.
OL,10,FA burglar who was given a second
OL,11,Fchance is now behind bars after he
OL,12,Fbroke into a shop for a second time
OL,13,Fjust weeks later.
OL,15,FStephen Rose broke into Drinks
OL,16,FExpress, on Adelaide Terrace, in the
OL,17,FBenwell area of Newcastle on 24
OL,18,FJanuary, stealing #600 in cash and
OL,19,F#500-worth of cigarettes.
