OL,6,FFollowing investigations by officers
OL,7,Fwith Northumbria Police's Response
OL,8,FPolicing Team, Rose was apprehended
OL,9,Fand charged with burglary.
OL,11,FTwo days later, at Newcastle
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court Rose pleaded guilty
OL,13,Fto the offence and was given a six-
OL,14,Fmonth prison sentence, suspended for
OL,15,F18 months.
