OL,6,FHowever, Rose did not learn his lesson
OL,7,Fand shortly before 1am on Thursday 15
OL,8,FFebruary, the owner of Drinks Express
OL,9,Fhad a notification on his mobile phone
OL,10,Fthat someone had again broken into his
OL,11,Fstore.
OL,13,FAfter breaking in through the ceiling,
OL,14,FRose stole the shop's till which
OL,15,Fcontained #200.
OL,17,FRose then dumped the till nearby
OL,18,Fbefore returning to his home address.
OL,19,FHe discarded the jacket he was wearing
OL,20,Fin the accommodation's communal area
OL,21,Fand it was later seized by officers.
