OL,6,FThe officers then found Rose and he
OL,7,Fwas arrested on suspicion of burglary
OL,8,F` within two hours of the crime being
OL,9,Fcommitted.
OL,11,FIn interview, he denied the offence
OL,12,Fbut was charged and the next day put
OL,13,Fbefore the same magistrates' court.
OL,15,FHere, the 46-year-old, of Atkinson
OL,16,FRoad, Newcastle, pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Fburglary and was jailed for a year.
