OL,6,FFollowing Rose's sentencing, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Craig Austin, of Northumbria
OL,8,FPolice's High Impact Team, said: "This
OL,9,Fwas a fantastic piece of police work
OL,10,Fbetween various teams ` from the
OL,11,Fresponse cops who attended the scene
OL,12,Fso quickly following the report of
OL,13,Fburglary coming in, to the detectives
OL,14,Fwho pulled together the case to secure
OL,15,Fhis conviction.
