OL,6,F"Rose has simply not learned his
OL,7,Flesson after being given a suspended
OL,8,Fsentence and has once again shown a
OL,9,Fcomplete disregard for his victim `
OL,10,Fwho he has targeted twice in a matter
OL,11,Fof weeks.
OL,13,F"We will not tolerate this kind of
OL,14,Fcriminality and we understand the
OL,15,Fimpact burglary can have on our
OL,16,Fcommunities.
